#: ../../../../docstring of numpy.char.chararray.imag:4
msgid ""
"Returns a view into the original array for complex arrays. For non-complex "
"arrays, returns a zero array of the same dtype. For ``object`` arrays "
"returns elementwise ``.imag`` or ``0`` if ``.imag`` is undefined."
msgstr ""

